Gentlemen,

During the Google Meet about TNMAN 26   some comms items were discussed
that needed clarification.

TACN? Radio =E2=80=93 The CG and Chief Simpson talked about these and it lo=
oks like
3RGT will require at least 4 for the Holston Defense Mission. This may
change due to taskings on the OPORD but will we receive some training and
is there a plan to get them to the 3RGT AO.

ATAK was discussed and 3RGT will need training and technical help setting
that up. We have lost most of our people with any training in this.How do
you want to set this up?

Starlink. Is there any chance of 3RGT getting a Starlink for the  ICP in Mt
Carmel? Internet would be useful.

Please note CSM Michael Rutherford is the new 3RGT S6 and should be
included in all comms discussions going forward.

Joseph Smith

LTC(TN)

3RGT XO

